{
  "video_id": "bNOiwgrZbPE",
  "title": "Suzanne Talhouk: Don't kill your language",
  "es": 0,
  "json": [
    {
      "index": 1,
      "start_time": 0.0,
      "end_time": 7000.0,
      "text": "Translator: khalid marbou Reviewer: Anwar Dafa-Alla"
    },
    {
      "index": 2,
      "start_time": 13295.0,
      "end_time": 14921.0,
      "text": "Good morning!"
    },
    {
      "index": 3,
      "start_time": 15340.0,
      "end_time": 17889.0,
      "text": "Are you awake?"
    },
    {
      "index": 4,
      "start_time": 18679.0,
      "end_time": 20982.0,
      "text": "They took my name tag, but I wanted to ask you,"
    },
    {
      "index": 5,
      "start_time": 21183.0,
      "end_time": 23773.0,
      "text": "did anyone here write their name on the tag in Arabic?"
    },
    {
      "index": 6,
      "start_time": 23900.0,
      "end_time": 29293.0,
      "text": "Anyone! No one? All right, no problem."
    },
    {
      "index": 7,
      "start_time": 29529.0,
      "end_time": 33492.0,
      "text": "Once upon a time, not long ago,"
    },
    {
      "index": 8,
      "start_time": 33632.0,
      "end_time": 38130.0,
      "text": "I was sitting in a restaurant with my friend, ordering food."
    },
    {
      "index": 9,
      "start_time": 38477.0,
      "end_time": 41997.0,
      "text": "So I looked at the waiter and said,"
    },
    {
      "index": 10,
      "start_time": 42870.0,
      "end_time": 44959.0,
      "text": "\"Do you have a menu (Arabic)?\""
    },
    {
      "index": 11,
      "start_time": 45683.0,
      "end_time": 49443.0,
      "text": "He looked at me strangely, thinking that he misheard."
    },
    {
      "index": 12,
      "start_time": 49633.0,
      "end_time": 51706.0,
      "text": "He said, \"Sorry? (English).\""
    },
    {
      "index": 13,
      "start_time": 52132.0,
      "end_time": 55550.0,
      "text": "I said, \"The menu (Arabic), please.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 14,
      "start_time": 56110.0,
      "end_time": 59403.0,
      "text": "He replied, \"Don&#39;t you know what they call it?\""
    },
    {
      "index": 15,
      "start_time": 59714.0,
      "end_time": 61700.0,
      "text": "\"I do.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 16,
      "start_time": 61133.0,
      "end_time": 64618.0,
      "text": "He said, \"No! It&#39;s called \"menu\" (English), or \"menu\" (French).\""
    },
    {
      "index": 17,
      "start_time": 64688.0,
      "end_time": 66613.0,
      "text": "Is the French pronunciation correct?"
    },
    {
      "index": 18,
      "start_time": 66663.0,
      "end_time": 69530.0,
      "text": "\"Come, come, take care of this one!\" said the waiter."
    },
    {
      "index": 19,
      "start_time": 69123.0,
      "end_time": 73358.0,
      "text": "He was disgusted when talking to me, as if he was saying to himself,"
    },
    {
      "index": 20,
      "start_time": 73458.0,
      "end_time": 77400.0,
      "text": "\"If this was the last girl on Earth, I wouldn&#39;t look at her!\""
    },
    {
      "index": 21,
      "start_time": 77450.0,
      "end_time": 79507.0,
      "text": "What&#39;s the meaning of saying \"menu\" in Arabic?"
    },
    {
      "index": 22,
      "start_time": 79578.0,
      "end_time": 87583.0,
      "text": "Two words made a Lebanese young man judge a girl as being backward"
    },
    {
      "index": 23,
      "start_time": 88323.0,
      "end_time": 90350.0,
      "text": "and ignorant."
    },
    {
      "index": 24,
      "start_time": 90820.0,
      "end_time": 95996.0,
      "text": "How could she speak that way?"
    },
    {
      "index": 25,
      "start_time": 96346.0,
      "end_time": 99310.0,
      "text": "At that moment, I started thinking."
    },
    {
      "index": 26,
      "start_time": 99590.0,
      "end_time": 100107.0,
      "text": "It made me mad."
    },
    {
      "index": 27,
      "start_time": 100152.0,
      "end_time": 101236.0,
      "text": "It definitely hurts!"
    },
    {
      "index": 28,
      "start_time": 101326.0,
      "end_time": 104390.0,
      "text": "I&#39;m denied the right to speak my own language in my own country?"
    },
    {
      "index": 29,
      "start_time": 104441.0,
      "end_time": 106312.0,
      "text": "Where could this happen?"
    },
    {
      "index": 30,
      "start_time": 106392.0,
      "end_time": 109672.0,
      "text": "How did we get here?"
    },
    {
      "index": 31,
      "start_time": 109732.0,
      "end_time": 113504.0,
      "text": "Well, while we are here, there are many people like me,"
    },
    {
      "index": 32,
      "start_time": 113674.0,
      "end_time": 117820.0,
      "text": "who would reach a stage in their lives, where they involuntarily give up"
    },
    {
      "index": 33,
      "start_time": 117132.0,
      "end_time": 119420.0,
      "text": "everything that has happened to them in the past,"
    },
    {
      "index": 34,
      "start_time": 119420.0,
      "end_time": 121559.0,
      "text": "just so they can say that they&#39;re modern"
    },
    {
      "index": 35,
      "start_time": 121699.0,
      "end_time": 123840.0,
      "text": "and civilized."
    },
    {
      "index": 36,
      "start_time": 123920.0,
      "end_time": 126745.0,
      "text": "Should I forget all my culture, thoughts,"
    },
    {
      "index": 37,
      "start_time": 126835.0,
      "end_time": 131440.0,
      "text": "intellect and all my memories?"
    },
    {
      "index": 38,
      "start_time": 131690.0,
      "end_time": 134995.0,
      "text": "Childhood stories might be the best memories we have of the war!"
    },
    {
      "index": 39,
      "start_time": 135118.0,
      "end_time": 140303.0,
      "text": "Should I forget everything I learned in Arabic, just to conform?"
    },
    {
      "index": 40,
      "start_time": 140423.0,
      "end_time": 143588.0,
      "text": "To be one of them?"
    },
    {
      "index": 41,
      "start_time": 143878.0,
      "end_time": 146220.0,
      "text": "Where&#39;s the logic in that?"
    },
    {
      "index": 42,
      "start_time": 146132.0,
      "end_time": 149690.0,
      "text": "Despite all that, I tried to understand him."
    },
    {
      "index": 43,
      "start_time": 149780.0,
      "end_time": 155946.0,
      "text": "I didn&#39;t want to judge him with the same cruelty that he judged me."
    },
    {
      "index": 44,
      "start_time": 155946.0,
      "end_time": 159712.0,
      "text": "The Arabic language doesn&#39;t satisfy today&#39;s needs."
    },
    {
      "index": 45,
      "start_time": 159902.0,
      "end_time": 161694.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s not a language for science,"
    },
    {
      "index": 46,
      "start_time": 161764.0,
      "end_time": 163215.0,
      "text": "research,"
    },
    {
      "index": 47,
      "start_time": 163275.0,
      "end_time": 165234.0,
      "text": "a language we&#39;re used to in universities,"
    },
    {
      "index": 48,
      "start_time": 165294.0,
      "end_time": 167374.0,
      "text": "a language we use in the workplace,"
    },
    {
      "index": 49,
      "start_time": 167694.0,
      "end_time": 173798.0,
      "text": "a language we rely on if we were to perform an advanced research project,"
    },
    {
      "index": 50,
      "start_time": 173888.0,
      "end_time": 176555.0,
      "text": "and it definitely isn&#39;t a language we use at the airport."
    },
    {
      "index": 51,
      "start_time": 176555.0,
      "end_time": 179360.0,
      "text": "If we did so, they&#39;d strip us of our clothes."
    },
    {
      "index": 52,
      "start_time": 180780.0,
      "end_time": 184328.0,
      "text": "Where can I use it, then? We could all ask this question!"
    },
    {
      "index": 53,
      "start_time": 184408.0,
      "end_time": 187980.0,
      "text": "So, you want us to use Arabic. Where are we to do so?"
    },
    {
      "index": 54,
      "start_time": 188660.0,
      "end_time": 191130.0,
      "text": "This is one reality."
    },
    {
      "index": 55,
      "start_time": 191240.0,
      "end_time": 196488.0,
      "text": "But we have another more important reality that we ought to think about."
    },
    {
      "index": 56,
      "start_time": 196878.0,
      "end_time": 199807.0,
      "text": "Arabic is the mother tongue."
    },
    {
      "index": 57,
      "start_time": 199867.0,
      "end_time": 205691.0,
      "text": "Research says that mastery of other languages"
    },
    {
      "index": 58,
      "start_time": 205718.0,
      "end_time": 209214.0,
      "text": "demands mastery of the mother tongue."
    },
    {
      "index": 59,
      "start_time": 209679.0,
      "end_time": 216344.0,
      "text": "Mastery of the mother tongue is a prerequisite for creative expression in other languages."
    },
    {
      "index": 60,
      "start_time": 216514.0,
      "end_time": 217819.0,
      "text": "How?"
    },
    {
      "index": 61,
      "start_time": 218199.0,
      "end_time": 219899.0,
      "text": "Gibran Khalil Gibran,"
    },
    {
      "index": 62,
      "start_time": 220489.0,
      "end_time": 224390.0,
      "text": "when he first started writing, he used Arabic."
    },
    {
      "index": 63,
      "start_time": 224540.0,
      "end_time": 230872.0,
      "text": "All his ideas, imagination and philosophy"
    },
    {
      "index": 64,
      "start_time": 231122.0,
      "end_time": 234589.0,
      "text": "were inspired by this little boy in the village"
    },
    {
      "index": 65,
      "start_time": 234869.0,
      "end_time": 236980.0,
      "text": "where he grew up, smelling a specific smell,"
    },
    {
      "index": 66,
      "start_time": 237150.0,
      "end_time": 238361.0,
      "text": "hearing a specific voice,"
    },
    {
      "index": 67,
      "start_time": 238421.0,
      "end_time": 239986.0,
      "text": "and thinking a specific thought."
    },
    {
      "index": 68,
      "start_time": 240206.0,
      "end_time": 244786.0,
      "text": "So, when he started writing in English, he had enough baggage."
    },
    {
      "index": 69,
      "start_time": 244917.0,
      "end_time": 247185.0,
      "text": "Even when he wrote in English,"
    },
    {
      "index": 70,
      "start_time": 247265.0,
      "end_time": 250976.0,
      "text": "when you read his writings in English, you smell the same smell,"
    },
    {
      "index": 71,
      "start_time": 251157.0,
      "end_time": 252871.0,
      "text": "sense the same feeling."
    },
    {
      "index": 72,
      "start_time": 253147.0,
      "end_time": 256733.0,
      "text": "You can imagine that that&#39;s him writing in English,"
    },
    {
      "index": 73,
      "start_time": 256813.0,
      "end_time": 262770.0,
      "text": "the same boy who came from the mountain. From a village on Mount Lebanon."
    },
    {
      "index": 74,
      "start_time": 262730.0,
      "end_time": 269910.0,
      "text": "So, this is an example no one can argue with."
    },
    {
      "index": 75,
      "start_time": 269401.0,
      "end_time": 273981.0,
      "text": "Second, it&#39;s often said that if you want to kill a nation,"
    },
    {
      "index": 76,
      "start_time": 274600.0,
      "end_time": 276841.0,
      "text": "the only way to kill a nation,"
    },
    {
      "index": 77,
      "start_time": 277600.0,
      "end_time": 278465.0,
      "text": "is to kill its language."
    },
    {
      "index": 78,
      "start_time": 278875.0,
      "end_time": 283995.0,
      "text": "This is a reality that developed societies are aware of."
    },
    {
      "index": 79,
      "start_time": 284352.0,
      "end_time": 290666.0,
      "text": "The Germans, French, Japanese and Chinese, all these nations are aware of this."
    },
    {
      "index": 80,
      "start_time": 290876.0,
      "end_time": 294712.0,
      "text": "That&#39;s why they legislate to protect their language."
    },
    {
      "index": 81,
      "start_time": 294842.0,
      "end_time": 297243.0,
      "text": "They make it sacred."
    },
    {
      "index": 82,
      "start_time": 297323.0,
      "end_time": 302830.0,
      "text": "That&#39;s why they use it in production, they pay a lot of money to develop it."
    },
    {
      "index": 83,
      "start_time": 303340.0,
      "end_time": 305705.0,
      "text": "Do we know better than them?"
    },
    {
      "index": 84,
      "start_time": 306116.0,
      "end_time": 307116.0,
      "text": "All right,"
    },
    {
      "index": 85,
      "start_time": 307122.0,
      "end_time": 308949.0,
      "text": "we aren&#39;t from the developed world,"
    },
    {
      "index": 86,
      "start_time": 308949.0,
      "end_time": 311167.0,
      "text": "this advanced thinking hasn&#39;t reached us yet,"
    },
    {
      "index": 87,
      "start_time": 311257.0,
      "end_time": 313901.0,
      "text": "and we would like to catch up with the civilized world."
    },
    {
      "index": 88,
      "start_time": 315181.0,
      "end_time": 319224.0,
      "text": "Countries that were once like us, but decided to strive for development,"
    },
    {
      "index": 89,
      "start_time": 319514.0,
      "end_time": 320950.0,
      "text": "do research,"
    },
    {
      "index": 90,
      "start_time": 321100.0,
      "end_time": 322933.0,
      "text": "and catch up with those countries,"
    },
    {
      "index": 91,
      "start_time": 322994.0,
      "end_time": 325773.0,
      "text": "such as Turkey, Malaysia and others,"
    },
    {
      "index": 92,
      "start_time": 325933.0,
      "end_time": 329604.0,
      "text": "they carried their language with them as they were climbing the ladder,"
    },
    {
      "index": 93,
      "start_time": 329724.0,
      "end_time": 333100.0,
      "text": "protected it like a diamond."
    },
    {
      "index": 94,
      "start_time": 333131.0,
      "end_time": 334640.0,
      "text": "They kept it close to them."
    },
    {
      "index": 95,
      "start_time": 334690.0,
      "end_time": 338940.0,
      "text": "Because if you get any product from Turkey or elsewhere"
    },
    {
      "index": 96,
      "start_time": 339300.0,
      "end_time": 341106.0,
      "text": "and it&#39;s not labeled in Turkish,"
    },
    {
      "index": 97,
      "start_time": 341616.0,
      "end_time": 344650.0,
      "text": "then it isn&#39;t a local product."
    },
    {
      "index": 98,
      "start_time": 344195.0,
      "end_time": 346778.0,
      "text": "You wouldn&#39;t believe it&#39;s a local product."
    },
    {
      "index": 99,
      "start_time": 347168.0,
      "end_time": 349640.0,
      "text": "They&#39;d go back to being consumers,"
    },
    {
      "index": 100,
      "start_time": 349800.0,
      "end_time": 355153.0,
      "text": "clueless consumers, like we are most of the time."
    },
    {
      "index": 101,
      "start_time": 355463.0,
      "end_time": 361334.0,
      "text": "So, in order for them to innovate and produce, they had to protect their language."
    },
    {
      "index": 102,
      "start_time": 363187.0,
      "end_time": 367521.0,
      "text": "If I say, \"Freedom, sovereignty, independence (Arabic),\""
    },
    {
      "index": 103,
      "start_time": 368101.0,
      "end_time": 370555.0,
      "text": "what does this remind you of?"
    },
    {
      "index": 104,
      "start_time": 372625.0,
      "end_time": 374241.0,
      "text": "It doesn&#39;t ring a bell, does it?"
    },
    {
      "index": 105,
      "start_time": 374819.0,
      "end_time": 378520.0,
      "text": "Regardless of the who, how and why."
    },
    {
      "index": 106,
      "start_time": 379580.0,
      "end_time": 385657.0,
      "text": "Language isn&#39;t just for conversing, just words coming out of our mouths."
    },
    {
      "index": 107,
      "start_time": 385798.0,
      "end_time": 390500.0,
      "text": "Language represents specific stages in our lives,"
    },
    {
      "index": 108,
      "start_time": 390690.0,
      "end_time": 395723.0,
      "text": "and terminology that is linked to our emotions."
    },
    {
      "index": 109,
      "start_time": 395723.0,
      "end_time": 398155.0,
      "text": "So when we say, \"Freedom, sovereignty, independence,\""
    },
    {
      "index": 110,
      "start_time": 398155.0,
      "end_time": 401565.0,
      "text": "each one of you draws a specific image in their own mind,"
    },
    {
      "index": 111,
      "start_time": 401778.0,
      "end_time": 404374.0,
      "text": "there are specific feelings"
    },
    {
      "index": 112,
      "start_time": 404444.0,
      "end_time": 407100.0,
      "text": "of a specific day in a specific historical period."
    },
    {
      "index": 113,
      "start_time": 407121.0,
      "end_time": 410424.0,
      "text": "Language isn&#39;t one, two or three words or letters put together."
    },
    {
      "index": 114,
      "start_time": 410765.0,
      "end_time": 413339.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s an idea inside that relates to how we think,"
    },
    {
      "index": 115,
      "start_time": 413339.0,
      "end_time": 419300.0,
      "text": "and how we see each other and how others see us."
    },
    {
      "index": 116,
      "start_time": 419300.0,
      "end_time": 420707.0,
      "text": "What is our intellect?"
    },
    {
      "index": 117,
      "start_time": 420977.0,
      "end_time": 423498.0,
      "text": "How do you say whether this guy understands or not?"
    },
    {
      "index": 118,
      "start_time": 423639.0,
      "end_time": 431368.0,
      "text": "So, if I say, \"Freedom, sovereignty, independence (English),\""
    },
    {
      "index": 119,
      "start_time": 432164.0,
      "end_time": 434152.0,
      "text": "or if your son came up to you and said,"
    },
    {
      "index": 120,
      "start_time": 434265.0,
      "end_time": 438851.0,
      "text": "\"Dad, have you lived through the period of the freedom (English) slogan?\""
    },
    {
      "index": 121,
      "start_time": 438971.0,
      "end_time": 440651.0,
      "text": "How would you feel?"
    },
    {
      "index": 122,
      "start_time": 441741.0,
      "end_time": 445465.0,
      "text": "If you don&#39;t see a problem,"
    },
    {
      "index": 123,
      "start_time": 445665.0,
      "end_time": 449144.0,
      "text": "then I&#39;d better leave, and stop talking in vain."
    },
    {
      "index": 124,
      "start_time": 449334.0,
      "end_time": 454600.0,
      "text": "The idea is that these expressions remind us of a specific thing."
    },
    {
      "index": 125,
      "start_time": 455250.0,
      "end_time": 460586.0,
      "text": "I have a francophone friend who&#39;s married to a French man."
    },
    {
      "index": 126,
      "start_time": 460946.0,
      "end_time": 464163.0,
      "text": "I asked her once how things were going."
    },
    {
      "index": 127,
      "start_time": 464253.0,
      "end_time": 465789.0,
      "text": "She said, \"Everything is fine,"
    },
    {
      "index": 128,
      "start_time": 465921.0,
      "end_time": 470370.0,
      "text": "but once, I spent a whole night asking and trying to translate"
    },
    {
      "index": 129,
      "start_time": 470370.0,
      "end_time": 472970.0,
      "text": "the meaning of the word &#39;toqborni&#39; for him.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 130,
      "start_time": 472970.0,
      "end_time": 474359.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 131,
      "start_time": 474385.0,
      "end_time": 477495.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    },
    {
      "index": 132,
      "start_time": 482130.0,
      "end_time": 485363.0,
      "text": "The poor woman had mistakenly told him \"toqborni,\""
    },
    {
      "index": 133,
      "start_time": 485483.0,
      "end_time": 488335.0,
      "text": "and then spent the whole night trying to explain it to him."
    },
    {
      "index": 134,
      "start_time": 488335.0,
      "end_time": 491863.0,
      "text": "He was puzzled by the thought: \"How could anyone be this cruel?"
    },
    {
      "index": 135,
      "start_time": 492930.0,
      "end_time": 493779.0,
      "text": "Does she want to commit suicide?"
    },
    {
      "index": 136,
      "start_time": 494369.0,
      "end_time": 496585.0,
      "text": "&#39;Bury me?&#39; (English)\""
    },
    {
      "index": 137,
      "start_time": 497850.0,
      "end_time": 499532.0,
      "text": "This is one of the few examples."
    },
    {
      "index": 138,
      "start_time": 499623.0,
      "end_time": 502772.0,
      "text": "It made us feel that she&#39;s unable to tell that word to her husband,"
    },
    {
      "index": 139,
      "start_time": 502772.0,
      "end_time": 505461.0,
      "text": "since he won&#39;t understand,"
    },
    {
      "index": 140,
      "start_time": 505461.0,
      "end_time": 508382.0,
      "text": "and he&#39;s right not to; his way of thinking is different."
    },
    {
      "index": 141,
      "start_time": 508862.0,
      "end_time": 512176.0,
      "text": "She said to me, \"He listens to Fairuz with me,"
    },
    {
      "index": 142,
      "start_time": 512446.0,
      "end_time": 516861.0,
      "text": "and one night, I tried to translate for him"
    },
    {
      "index": 143,
      "start_time": 516991.0,
      "end_time": 520250.0,
      "text": "so he can feel what I feel when I listen to Fairuz.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 144,
      "start_time": 520308.99999999994,
      "end_time": 522499.99999999994,
      "text": "The poor woman tried to translate this for him:"
    },
    {
      "index": 145,
      "start_time": 522590.00000000006,
      "end_time": 526695.0,
      "text": "\"From them I extended my hands and stole you --\""
    },
    {
      "index": 146,
      "start_time": 526755.0,
      "end_time": 527830.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 147,
      "start_time": 528000.0,
      "end_time": 529405.0,
      "text": "And here&#39;s the pickle:"
    },
    {
      "index": 148,
      "start_time": 529405.0,
      "end_time": 533500.0,
      "text": "\"And because you belong to them, I returned my hands and left you.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 149,
      "start_time": 533500.0,
      "end_time": 534616.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 150,
      "start_time": 534765.0,
      "end_time": 536800.0,
      "text": "Translate that for me."
    },
    {
      "index": 151,
      "start_time": 536140.0,
      "end_time": 543674.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    },
    {
      "index": 152,
      "start_time": 543804.0,
      "end_time": 547848.0,
      "text": "So, what have we done to protect the Arabic language?"
    },
    {
      "index": 153,
      "start_time": 548129.0,
      "end_time": 551265.0,
      "text": "We turned this into a concern of the civil society,"
    },
    {
      "index": 154,
      "start_time": 551495.0,
      "end_time": 554199.0,
      "text": "and we launched a campaign to preserve the Arabic language."
    },
    {
      "index": 155,
      "start_time": 554279.0,
      "end_time": 557594.0,
      "text": "Even though many people told me, \"Why do you bother?"
    },
    {
      "index": 156,
      "start_time": 557644.0,
      "end_time": 560677.0,
      "text": "Forget about this headache and go have fun.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 157,
      "start_time": 560717.0,
      "end_time": 562254.0,
      "text": "No problem!"
    },
    {
      "index": 158,
      "start_time": 562434.0,
      "end_time": 565526.0,
      "text": "The campaign to preserve Arabic launched a slogan that says,"
    },
    {
      "index": 159,
      "start_time": 565527.0,
      "end_time": 568360.0,
      "text": "\"I talk to you from the East, but you reply from the West.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 160,
      "start_time": 568620.0,
      "end_time": 575928.0,
      "text": "We didn&#39;t say, \"No! We do not accept this or that.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 161,
      "start_time": 576188.0,
      "end_time": 581530.0,
      "text": "We didn&#39;t adopt this style because that way, we wouldn&#39;t be understood."
    },
    {
      "index": 162,
      "start_time": 581203.0,
      "end_time": 584646.0,
      "text": "And when someone talks to me that way, I hate the Arabic language."
    },
    {
      "index": 163,
      "start_time": 584947.0,
      "end_time": 586279.0,
      "text": "We say--"
    },
    {
      "index": 164,
      "start_time": 586359.0,
      "end_time": 589181.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    },
    {
      "index": 165,
      "start_time": 589271.0,
      "end_time": 591652.0,
      "text": "We want to change our reality,"
    },
    {
      "index": 166,
      "start_time": 591703.0,
      "end_time": 596385.0,
      "text": "and be convinced in a way that reflects our dreams, aspirations and day-to-day life."
    },
    {
      "index": 167,
      "start_time": 596655.0,
      "end_time": 601949.0,
      "text": "In a way that dresses like us and thinks like we do."
    },
    {
      "index": 168,
      "start_time": 601950.0,
      "end_time": 604823.0,
      "text": "So, \"I talk to you from the East, but you reply from the West\""
    },
    {
      "index": 169,
      "start_time": 604823.0,
      "end_time": 606476.0,
      "text": "has hit the spot."
    },
    {
      "index": 170,
      "start_time": 606476.0,
      "end_time": 610169.0,
      "text": "Something very easy, yet creative and persuasive."
    },
    {
      "index": 171,
      "start_time": 610579.0,
      "end_time": 613676.0,
      "text": "After that, we launched another campaign"
    },
    {
      "index": 172,
      "start_time": 614277.0,
      "end_time": 617685.0,
      "text": "with scenes of letters on the ground."
    },
    {
      "index": 173,
      "start_time": 617795.0,
      "end_time": 620103.0,
      "text": "You&#39;ve seen an example of it outside,"
    },
    {
      "index": 174,
      "start_time": 620284.0,
      "end_time": 624665.0,
      "text": "a scene of a letter surrounded by black and yellow tape"
    },
    {
      "index": 175,
      "start_time": 624666.0,
      "end_time": 627508.0,
      "text": "with \"Don&#39;t kill your language!\" written on it."
    },
    {
      "index": 176,
      "start_time": 627508.0,
      "end_time": 631122.0,
      "text": "Why? Seriously, don&#39;t kill your language."
    },
    {
      "index": 177,
      "start_time": 631212.0,
      "end_time": 634126.0,
      "text": "We really shouldn&#39;t kill our language."
    },
    {
      "index": 178,
      "start_time": 634266.0,
      "end_time": 639304.0,
      "text": "If we were to kill the language, we&#39;d have to find an identity."
    },
    {
      "index": 179,
      "start_time": 639424.0,
      "end_time": 641313.0,
      "text": "We&#39;d have to find an existence."
    },
    {
      "index": 180,
      "start_time": 641383.0,
      "end_time": 643698.0,
      "text": "We&#39;d go back to the beginning."
    },
    {
      "index": 181,
      "start_time": 643768.0,
      "end_time": 650260.0,
      "text": "This is beyond just missing our chance of being modern and civilized."
    },
    {
      "index": 182,
      "start_time": 651260.0,
      "end_time": 657200.0,
      "text": "After that we released photos of guys and girls wearing the Arabic letter."
    },
    {
      "index": 183,
      "start_time": 657620.0,
      "end_time": 660133.0,
      "text": "Photos of \"cool\" guys and girls."
    },
    {
      "index": 184,
      "start_time": 660263.0,
      "end_time": 662424.0,
      "text": "We are very cool!"
    },
    {
      "index": 185,
      "start_time": 662904.0,
      "end_time": 667198.0,
      "text": "And to whoever might say, \"Ha! You used an English word!\""
    },
    {
      "index": 186,
      "start_time": 667278.0,
      "end_time": 671700.0,
      "text": "I say, \"No! I adopt the word &#39;cool.&#39;\""
    },
    {
      "index": 187,
      "start_time": 671120.0,
      "end_time": 674865.0,
      "text": "Let them object however they want, but give me a word that&#39;s nicer"
    },
    {
      "index": 188,
      "start_time": 674895.0,
      "end_time": 677531.0,
      "text": "and matches the reality better."
    },
    {
      "index": 189,
      "start_time": 677591.0,
      "end_time": 679565.0,
      "text": "I will keep on saying \"Internet\""
    },
    {
      "index": 190,
      "start_time": 679565.0,
      "end_time": 682389.0,
      "text": "I wouldn&#39;t say: \"I&#39;m going to the world wide web\""
    },
    {
      "index": 191,
      "start_time": 682399.0,
      "end_time": 684175.0,
      "text": "(Laughs)"
    },
    {
      "index": 192,
      "start_time": 684175.0,
      "end_time": 687445.0,
      "text": "Because it doesn&#39;t fit! We shouldn&#39;t kid ourselves."
    },
    {
      "index": 193,
      "start_time": 687686.0,
      "end_time": 691355.0,
      "text": "But to reach this point, we all have to be convinced"
    },
    {
      "index": 194,
      "start_time": 691885.0,
      "end_time": 694200.0,
      "text": "that we shouldn&#39;t allow anyone who is bigger"
    },
    {
      "index": 195,
      "start_time": 694200.0,
      "end_time": 697356.0,
      "text": "or thinks they have any authority over us when it comes to language,"
    },
    {
      "index": 196,
      "start_time": 697356.0,
      "end_time": 702814.0,
      "text": "to control us or make us think and feel what they want."
    },
    {
      "index": 197,
      "start_time": 703685.0,
      "end_time": 707443.0,
      "text": "Creativity is the idea."
    },
    {
      "index": 198,
      "start_time": 707653.0,
      "end_time": 710213.0,
      "text": "So, if we can&#39;t reach space or build a rocket and so on,"
    },
    {
      "index": 199,
      "start_time": 710213.0,
      "end_time": 712113.0,
      "text": "we can be creative."
    },
    {
      "index": 200,
      "start_time": 712113.0,
      "end_time": 715880.0,
      "text": "At this moment, every one of you is a creative project."
    },
    {
      "index": 201,
      "start_time": 715950.0,
      "end_time": 718468.0,
      "text": "Creativity in your mother tongue is the path."
    },
    {
      "index": 202,
      "start_time": 718798.0,
      "end_time": 722244.0,
      "text": "Let&#39;s start from this moment."
    },
    {
      "index": 203,
      "start_time": 722534.0,
      "end_time": 724536.0,
      "text": "Let&#39;s write a novel or produce a short film."
    },
    {
      "index": 204,
      "start_time": 724596.0,
      "end_time": 727874.0,
      "text": "A single novel could make us global again."
    },
    {
      "index": 205,
      "start_time": 727934.0,
      "end_time": 731699.0,
      "text": "It could bring the Arabic language back to being number one."
    },
    {
      "index": 206,
      "start_time": 732380.0,
      "end_time": 736231.0,
      "text": "So, it&#39;s not true that there&#39;s no solution; there is a solution!"
    },
    {
      "index": 207,
      "start_time": 736231.0,
      "end_time": 740230.0,
      "text": "But we have to know that, and be convinced that a solution exists,"
    },
    {
      "index": 208,
      "start_time": 740230.0,
      "end_time": 743229.0,
      "text": "that we have a duty to be part of that solution."
    },
    {
      "index": 209,
      "start_time": 743929.0,
      "end_time": 746716.0,
      "text": "In conclusion, what can you do today?"
    },
    {
      "index": 210,
      "start_time": 746836.0,
      "end_time": 750000.0,
      "text": "Now, tweets, who&#39;s tweeting?"
    },
    {
      "index": 211,
      "start_time": 752600.0,
      "end_time": 757334.0,
      "text": "Please, I beg of you, even though my time has finished,"
    },
    {
      "index": 212,
      "start_time": 757430.0,
      "end_time": 762487.0,
      "text": "either Arabic, English, French or Chinese."
    },
    {
      "index": 213,
      "start_time": 762577.0,
      "end_time": 768158.0,
      "text": "But don&#39;t write Arabic with Latin characters mixed with numbers!"
    },
    {
      "index": 214,
      "start_time": 768298.0,
      "end_time": 772358.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    },
    {
      "index": 215,
      "start_time": 772408.0,
      "end_time": 775556.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s a disaster! That&#39;s not a language."
    },
    {
      "index": 216,
      "start_time": 775866.0,
      "end_time": 779412.0,
      "text": "You&#39;d be entering a virtual world with a virtual language."
    },
    {
      "index": 217,
      "start_time": 779562.0,
      "end_time": 782244.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s not easy to come back from such a place and rise."
    },
    {
      "index": 218,
      "start_time": 782724.0,
      "end_time": 784806.0,
      "text": "That&#39;s the first thing we can do."
    },
    {
      "index": 219,
      "start_time": 784896.0,
      "end_time": 787498.0,
      "text": "Second, there are many other things that we can do."
    },
    {
      "index": 220,
      "start_time": 787499.0,
      "end_time": 789904.0,
      "text": "We&#39;re not here today to convince each other."
    },
    {
      "index": 221,
      "start_time": 789904.0,
      "end_time": 793438.0,
      "text": "We&#39;re here to bring attention to the necessity of preserving this language."
    },
    {
      "index": 222,
      "start_time": 793438.0,
      "end_time": 796313.0,
      "text": "Now I will tell you a secret."
    },
    {
      "index": 223,
      "start_time": 797303.0,
      "end_time": 802490.0,
      "text": "A baby first identifies its father"
    },
    {
      "index": 224,
      "start_time": 802490.0,
      "end_time": 804557.0,
      "text": "through language."
    },
    {
      "index": 225,
      "start_time": 804557.0,
      "end_time": 809716.0,
      "text": "When my daughter is born, I&#39;ll tell her, \"This is your father, honey (Arabic).\""
    },
    {
      "index": 226,
      "start_time": 809796.0,
      "end_time": 814324.0,
      "text": "I wouldn&#39;t say, \"This is your dad, honey (English).\""
    },
    {
      "index": 227,
      "start_time": 814585.0,
      "end_time": 817770.0,
      "text": "And in the supermarket, I promise my daughter Noor,"
    },
    {
      "index": 228,
      "start_time": 817770.0,
      "end_time": 819986.0,
      "text": "that if she says to me, \"Thanks (Arabic),\""
    },
    {
      "index": 229,
      "start_time": 820860.0,
      "end_time": 824753.0,
      "text": "I won&#39;t say, \"Dis, &#39;Merci, Maman,&#39;\" and hope no one has heard her."
    },
    {
      "index": 230,
      "start_time": 824813.0,
      "end_time": 827900.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    },
    {
      "index": 231,
      "start_time": 835980.0,
      "end_time": 840877.0,
      "text": "Let&#39;s get rid of this cultural cringe."
    },
    {
      "index": 232,
      "start_time": 841297.0,
      "end_time": 844343.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    }
  ]
}